              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Cylindrical ionization chambers containing",
                "  a thin flat foil of material for measurement."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Fission chamber for U-235 monitor analogous",
                "        for that of Lithium.",
                " Fission and lithium counters were clamped together so",
                " that foils were concentric and separated only by the",
                " thickness of counter walls aprx. 0.1 cm. Counter runs",
                " were repeated with that assembly rotated through 180",
                " degree about the line perpendicular to the neutron",
                " beam."
              ]
