                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 950 barns at 0.025 eV,",
                " from absorption xsec of natural Li given in MONIT-REF",
                " Count rates from Li-d were actually measured relative",
                " to the rate from U-235 at 25, 67 and 100 keV. The xs",
                " for U-235(N,F) at these energies are not given. The",
                " above cross sections at 0.025 eV were used to make",
                " the method independent of the mass of material in each",
                " sample, the mass of U-235 being known."
              ]
            }
          ],
