                " A U-235 foil of aprx. 0.3 milligram/cm2 over an area",
                " of 8 cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Corrections were made for neutron attenuation and",
                " scattering in counters, for the small anisotropy due",
                " to center-of-mass motion, for background due to room",
                " scattering, for alpha-particle and triton absorption",
                " in foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
